OL,3,CBelfast set for jobs boost with #700
OL,4,Cmillion plan on way
OL,6,FBelfast is set to benefit from a Civil
OL,7,FService shake-up as the UK Government
OL,8,Fannounces plans to relocate thousands
OL,9,Fof roles from London to 13 regional
OL,10,Fhubs across the country.
OL,12,FThe move is projected to bring a #729
OL,13,Fmillion economic boost to the regional
OL,14,Fareas by 2030.
OL,16,FAs part of the initiative, Belfast
OL,17,Fjoins cities including Birmingham,
OL,18,FCardiff, Edinburgh, and Glasgow, which
OL,19,Fare also set to receive the job boost.
