OL,3,CBelfast set for jobs boost with #700
OL,4,Cmillion plan on way
OL,6,FThis follows backing from Prime
OL,7,FMinister Keir Starmer to ensure the
OL,8,FCivil Service contributes to local
OL,9,Fgrowth and job creation.
OL,11,F"To deliver our Plan for Change, we
OL,12,Fare taking more decision-making out of
OL,13,FWhitehall and moving it closer to
OL,14,Fcommunities all across the UK," said
OL,15,Fthe Chancellor of the Duchy of
OL,16,FLancaster.
