OL,3,CBelfast set for jobs boost with #700
OL,4,Cmillion plan on way
OL,6,FPat McFadden continued: "By relocating
OL,7,Fthousands of Civil Service roles we
OL,8,Fwill not only save taxpayers money, we
OL,9,Fwill make this Government one that
OL,10,Fbetter reflects the country it serves.
OL,11,FWe will also be making sure that
OL,12,FGovernment jobs support economic
OL,13,Fgrowth throughout the country.
OL,15,F"As we radically reform the state, we
OL,16,Fare going to make it much easier for
OL,17,Ftalented people everywhere to join the
OL,18,FCivil Service and help us rebuild
OL,19,FBritain."
