OL,3,CBelfast set for jobs boost with #700
OL,4,Cmillion plan on way
OL,6,FCurrently, 3,330 civil service roles
OL,7,Fare based in Belfast with over 4,470
OL,8,Ffull time equivalent roles based in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FGovernment departments now will submit
OL,12,Fplans for how many roles they plan to
OL,13,Fmove to each of the locations as part
OL,14,Fof the spending review.
OL,16,FWithin the reshuffle, plans for 50% of
OL,17,Fall UK-based Senior Civil Servants
OL,18,Fwill be located in regional offices by
OL,19,F2030 have been finalised, to help
OL,20,Fensure equal opportunities for those
OL,21,Foutside of London.
